videos.description: Jordan Goldwire steals the rock and Elijah Harkless lays it in to regain the lead.
videos.headline: Jordan Goldwire's steal leads to an Oklahoma basket

videos.description: Jalen Hill is smooth as silk as he spins off of his defender and knocks down the floater for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Jalen Hill puts his defender in the spin cycle and drains the floater for Oklahoma

videos.description: Jase Febres hauls in the dime from Christian Bishop and lays it in to extend the Longhorns' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Christian Bishop with the absolute dime to Jase Febres for a Texas bucket) 2022/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Christian Bishop with the absolute dime to Jase Febres for a Texas bucket

videos.description: Elijah Harkless gets the steal and finishes with the reverse layup to regain the lead.
videos.headline: Elijah Harkless gets it done on both sides of the ball for Oklahoma

videos.description: Andrew Jones gathers the dime from Christian Bishop and drains the 3-pointer to extend the Longhorns' lead late in the first half.
videos.headline: Christian Bishop finds a wide-open Andrew Jones for a Texas 3

videos.description: Jalen Hill spins off of his defender and drains the and-1 to tie the game at 32-32.
videos.headline: Jalen Hill posts up his defender and drains the and-1

videos.description: Timmy Allen won't be denied as he snags the offensive rebound and knocks down the and-1 to regain the lead.
videos.headline: Timmy Allen snags the offensive board and drains the and-1 for Texas

videos.description: It's showtime in Norman, Oklahoma as Elijah Harkless steals the rock and fakes out his defender for the layup to pull the Sooners within four.
videos.headline: OU's Elijah Harkless completely fakes out defender to score

videos.description: Jordan Goldwire dives into the paint and lays it in to tie the game at 66-66, sending it into overtime.
videos.headline: OU's Jordan Goldwire drains the clutch basket to send the game into OT

videos.description: Timmy Allen flies to the rim and tips in the rock to help lead Texas past Oklahoma in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Timmy Allen soars through the paint and wins it for Texas in OT) 2022/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Timmy Allen soars through the paint to give Texas some insurance in OT
